article_title: LeGarrette Blount is back with the Pats!
article_summary: Looks like more Blount Force Trauma in Foxborough. The Boston Globe has confirmed the Patriots are bringing back running back LeGarrette Blount who is expected to sign a two-year deal for the veteran minimum salary plus incentives.

article_title: Barley to Blame for Tibetans Moving to Higher Altitudes
article_summary: Barley does incredibly well in colder climes, and with shortened growing seasons. This crop allowed the Tibetans to venture further and further up into the mountains.
